Wildrider/Speedbreaker/Beastbox

Wildrider jumped back from the computer screen, as the alarms going 
off suprised him after the long moments of silence. "Ha ha h, look 
alive Stunticons, we got's ourselves an invader" he said through a 
drooling smile, "Yah, should we go?" He turned asking Speedbreaker. 

"Why not, Megatron would give us slag if we didnt," He said while 
transforming into his car mode, and started reving his engine. "All 
right then, I'm off," he sped off towards the exit. Wildrider ran over 
to Dead-End's cr chamber and opened it. He was at 80%, the rest would 
heal manually, "Come on", he said pulling out an energon cube, and 
transforming following Speedbreaker.
